title: The Disappearance of Ashley, Kansas
itunes:title: The Disappearance of Ashley, Kansas
itunes:subtitle: The Creepypasta Anthology
description:
Sometime during the night of August 16, 1952, the small town of Ashley, Kansas ceased to exist, but that's only the beginning of the story. 

***

Guest narration thanks to Corinne Sanders and Nichole Goodnight

***

Please consider supporting the podcast at Patreon.com/Creepypod

***
